{"tid":1854330,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［我係醫護］我就黎頂唔順","createTime":"2020-01-31T12:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T04:32:47.000Z","uid":181549,"like":138,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"b10d1cfda36cc0d8eb8e835f5e44de482579e6d0","tid":1854330,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:07:10.000Z","msg":"我就快頂唔順<br />\n一個醫院一間隔離病房根本就唔夠應付班大陸西<br />\n未來十日又有第二批人要調去開多個隔離病房<br />\n我做到飯都無得食<br />\n水又無得飲<br />\n<br />\n個個大陸人（尤其啲身分證R/M字頭果班）<br />\n入到黎都唔合作 問親啲野又唔肯答<br />\n就算答你都係作野多<br />\n<br />\n有個case去完大陸醫院 睇完一次病<br />\n大陸照撚完張Xray就放走佢<br />\n而家個肺花多左又放佢走<br />\n佢就落黎香港醫<br />\n發燒唔退 我做護士同你抽組織要共處一室起碼30分鐘<br />\n<br />\n又有個case<br />\n話自己去過街市<br />\n不過去街市淨係買個膠袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲好意思話「我都唔知個街市有咩賣」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我屌你老母我仲要收幾多呢啲垃圾<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你班死中國人幾撚時死呀</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家根本唔再係隔離病房同事=dirty team<br />\n屌你做medical收啲隱形病人都好撚危險<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位，<br />\n請加入自己行業工會<br />\n求下你地全力支援醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地無退路 求下你地<br />\n我2月3-7號都會罷工<br />\n求你地同我地行呢條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11a07c5d2943819086b149ad1cd69f946883c94","tid":1854330,"uid":113187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:10:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a715f1f0eb1d3fec324808ece209cc14d3b0d1d","tid":1854330,"uid":317233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:11:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">武肺背後嘅第三次世界大戰：諜戰丶生化戰丶經濟戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1854117\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1854117</a><br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"21fee55fe17909d90f378622c1fb982d1b1caf38","tid":1854330,"uid":181549,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:13:00.000Z","msg":"一日唔封關<br />\n一日開幾多個隔離病房都係一鳩樣"},{"pid":"ecd6564da389ae0d9b87749ca1a5d04864aa8e1a","tid":1854330,"uid":54995,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:19:35.000Z","msg":"講到咁辛苦都仲要2月3先罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />祝你喺罷工之前就中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c08299bd27b8a1d1cedeb7477d47c664be1cd4","tid":1854330,"uid":113187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:19:49.000Z","msg":"屌你老母仆街政府<br />\n連官方口罩存量都唔撚夠膽講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11271f9dd2bcf90a712fb8c1c038a3d0a6f27695","tid":1854330,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:20:38.000Z","msg":"仆街蝗"},{"pid":"5a00966ed032f4ea0eea919beed3cd9e7f0628f6","tid":1854330,"uid":113187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:20:44.000Z","msg":"口罩存量仲少撚過當年SARS<br />\n17 年黎做撚過D咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9574bb2c77b9c522234f47b60ac260c3161479cb","tid":1854330,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:21:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">醫護界資源比狗隊少</span></strong><br />\nblue object <span style=\"color: red;\">24,110元 至 38,580元 </span><br />\nwhite object <span style=\"color: gold;\">45,305元 至 84,250元</span> <br />\n<br />\n三B級病人服務助理<span style=\"color: red;\">11,866元至14,064元</span><br />\n一級病人服務助理<span style=\"color: red;\">21,389元至25,199元</span><br />\n現時醫管局約有25,000名病人服務助理、運作助理及行政助理。<br />\n<br />\nEN <span style=\"color: red;\">20,610 至 43,783</span><br />\nRN <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">32,675 至 52,578</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">仇恨</span></strong><br />\n大半年打壓知識份子<br />\n當中不少醫護人士被打拉射告<br />\n而家就有事求人<br />\n<br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">無保障</span></strong><br />\n封關只係其中一樣<br />\n大劣病人根本唔守規矩<br />\n人地支那都識立法保護醫護人員<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/mobile/bkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200130%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMckuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=39347b7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/mobile/bkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html</a><br />\n而且不幸染病死左只有50萬賠償真係on9<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">對應解決方法</span></span><br />\n1.cut 狗隊資源及一半人工<br />\n提升醫護界薪金2倍<br />\n<br />\n2.答應五大訴求，追究警暴，放義士，<br />\n高官問責，實行雙普選，減仇恨<br />\n<br />\n3.提升醫護個人裝備，立法限制病人行為<br />\n立即全面封關，賠償額提升到500萬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">根本你做少一樣，醫護都唔會開工</span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"108c9450b4fcd795ad554d4127243c622642b9db","tid":1854330,"uid":194399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:22:07.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"da4b5587ad17d05485211abd5da07929616b8ae9","tid":1854330,"uid":9640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ecd6564da389ae0d9b87749ca1a5d04864aa8e1a","tid":1854330,"uid":54995,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T12:19:35.000Z","msg":"講到咁辛苦都仲要2月3先罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />祝你喺罷工之前就中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.